skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dog sounds
des:
This skill plays a variety of dog sounds! Let's raise the woof! Start up this skill and you will howl for more!

There are many different sounds and dog puns for your listening pleasure. After each sound is played, you can hear another by answering, "yes," or you can just woof!

To start the fun, simply say, "Alexa, open dog sounds!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
